            "enlarge_text": false,
            "text": "<h1>TRLab Privacy Policy</h1><p>Last updated: [11, 2025]</p><h2>1. Information We Collect</h2><h3>a. Device Information</h3><p>When you visit our Site, we automatically collect certain information about your device, including your browser type and version, IP address, time zone, installed cookies, viewed pages or products, referring websites or search terms, and how you interact with the Site.</p><p>We collect this data through:</p><ul><li><strong>Cookies</strong> — Small files stored on your device. <a href=\"http://www.allaboutcookies.org\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a> about cookies and how to disable them.</li><li><strong>Log files</strong> — Record actions on the Site (IP address, browser type, ISP, etc.).</li><li><strong>Web beacons / pixels / tags</strong> — Track browsing behavior and marketing performance.</li></ul><h3>b. Order Information</h3><p>When you make or attempt to make a purchase, we collect the following information:</p><ul><li>Name</li><li>Billing and shipping address</li><li>Payment information (including credit card numbers)</li><li>Email address and phone number</li></ul><p>Together, we refer to Device and Order Information as <strong>“Personal Information.”</strong></p><h2>2. How We Use Your Personal Information</h2><p>We use your information to:</p><ul><li>Process and fulfill your orders (payment, shipping, confirmations).</li><li>Communicate with you regarding your order or inquiries.</li><li>Screen for potential risks or fraudulent transactions.</li><li>Improve and optimize our Site and services.</li><li>Provide marketing updates or offers, if you have opted in.</li></ul><h2>3. Sharing Your Personal Information</h2><p>We share Personal Information only with trusted third parties necessary to operate our business:</p><ul><li><strong>Shopify</strong> — Powers our online store. <a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/legal/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Shopify Privacy Policy</a></li><li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — Helps us understand website usage. <a href=\"https://www.google.com/policies/privacy/\" target=\"_blank\">Google Privacy Policy</a><br/>Opt out: <a href=\"https://www.google.com/settings/ads/anonymous\" target=\"_blank\">Google Ads Settings</a> or <a href=\"http://optout.aboutads.info/\" target=\"_blank\">DAA opt-out portal</a>.</li></ul><p>We may also share information to comply with legal obligations, respond to lawful requests, or protect our rights.</p><h2>4. Targeted Advertising</h2><p>We may use your information to show relevant ads based on your preferences. You can opt out via:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.google.com/settings/ads/anonymous\" target=\"_blank\">Google Ads Settings</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.networkadvertising.org/understanding-online-advertising/how-does-it-work\" target=\"_blank\">Network Advertising Initiative</a></li></ul><h2>5. Do Not Track</h2><p>Our Site does not alter its data collection practices when a “Do Not Track” signal is received from your browser.</p><h2>6. Your Rights</h2><p>If you are located in the <strong>European Economic Area (EEA)</strong>, you have the right to:</p><ul><li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li><li>Request correction, update, or deletion of your data.</li><li>Withdraw consent to marketing communications.</li></ul><p>We process your data to fulfill contracts (e.g., order fulfillment) or pursue legitimate business interests. Your information may be transferred outside the EEA, including to Canada or the United States, under lawful safeguards.</p><h2>7. Data Retention</h2><p>We retain Order Information for our business records unless you request its deletion.</p><h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2><p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect operational, legal, or regulatory changes. The updated version will be effective upon publication on this page.</p><h2>9. Contact Us</h2><p>For any questions, concerns, or complaints about our privacy practices, please contact us:</p><p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:Sale@trlab.com\" title=\"mailto:Sale@trlab.com\">Sale@trlab.com</a></p><p>© TRLab. All rights reserved.</p>"
          }
